  },
  "description": "Status of the LLM agents (codex spawns) March drives: are they up, how much do they cost, how long do they take, and what work they run. The 'Agent — UP/DOWN' tile flips to DOWN on codex auth failure ('refresh token already used') — re-authenticate the agent. Backed by march_spawn_agent_failures_total / march_spawn_tokens_* / march_spawn_runs_total / march_spawn_duration_seconds and the legate circuit-breaker gauges (Prometheus).",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [
    { "asDropdown": false, "icon": "external link", "tags": [], "targetBlank": false, "title": "Spawn observability", "type": "link", "url": "/d/march-spawns" },
    { "asDropdown": false, "icon": "external link", "tags": [], "targetBlank": false, "title": "Legate loop service", "type": "link", "url": "/d/march-legate" }
  ],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Agent health",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "UP unless the agent is failing authentication (codex 'refresh token already used') in the last 10m, OR the legate circuit-breaker has paused dispatch for a hard-down agent. DOWN ⇒ re-authenticate the agent (codex login), then recover the backlog.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "color": "green", "index": 1, "text": "UP" }, "1": { "color": "red", "index": 0, "text": "DOWN — re-auth agent" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "value"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.2.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "clamp_max(max(march_legate_spawn_breaker_open) + (sum(rate(march_spawn_agent_failures_total{reason=\"auth\", backend=~\"$backend\", profile=~\"$profile\"}[10m])) or vector(0)), 1)",
          "legendFormat": "agent",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Agent — UP/DOWN",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Backpressure circuit-breaker. OPEN means the legate detected the agent is hard-down and PAUSED fresh dispatch (effective cap 0) so it stops flooding doomed spawns.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "color": "green", "index": 1, "text": "CLOSED" }, "1": { "color": "red", "index": 0, "text": "OPEN — dispatch paused" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 1 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "value"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.2.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "max(march_legate_spawn_breaker_open)",
          "legendFormat": "breaker",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Dispatch circuit-breaker",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Share of spawn dispatches that completed successfully, over the dashboard time range.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [],
          "max": 1,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "red", "value": null }, { "color": "orange", "value": 0.8 }, { "color": "green", "value": 0.95 } ] },
          "unit": "percentunit"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 1 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.2.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(increase(march_spawn_runs_total{backend=~\"$backend\", task_type=~\"$task_type\", profile=~\"$profile\", outcome=\"success\"}[$__range])) / clamp_min(sum(increase(march_spawn_runs_total{backend=~\"$backend\", task_type=~\"$task_type\", profile=~\"$profile\"}[$__range])), 1)",
          "legendFormat": "success rate",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Spawn success rate",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Agent failures by reason in range. 'auth' is the codex re-authentication signal.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }, "mappings": [], "unit": "short" },
        "overrides": [ { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "auth" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } } ] } ]
